106
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:25,110
So I have an idea,
Pointer.

107
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:27,540
Er...
What is that,

108
00:05:27,540 --> 00:05:29,430
your Bumbleness?

109
00:05:29,420 --> 00:05:33,790
<i>LET'S GO TO FLUTTER VALLEY
AND GET IT BACK!</i>

110
00:05:38,850 --> 00:05:42,060
(Stonebacks snorts)

111
