112
00:05:52,230 --> 00:05:54,320
We'll never make it in time.

113
00:05:54,310 --> 00:05:57,650
Oh, Flutter Valley
is going to wilt away.

114
00:05:57,650 --> 00:05:59,030
Don't give up,
Flutter Ponies.

115
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:02,910
There's still time to get
the Sunstone in place.

116
00:06:02,910 --> 00:06:05,000
Don't forget the witches.

117
00:06:04,990 --> 00:06:06,040
What about them?

118
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,460
Oh,
I forgot to tell you,

119
00:06:07,460 --> 00:06:10,040
the witches have
taken over Flutter Valley.

120
00:06:10,050 --> 00:06:11,640
Oh no!

121
00:06:11,630 --> 00:06:14,630
I'll go to Furbobia,
and get the rest of the Furbobs.

122
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:15,830
Maybe they can help.

123
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:20,350
Hop on, Furbob!
I'll get you there in no time.

124
00:06:20,340 --> 00:06:22,220
Meet you all at Flutter Valley.

125
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:25,850
Not that way,
this way.

126
00:06:25,850 --> 00:06:27,440
(buzz)

127
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:30,930
It's a race against the sun,
Flutter Ponies. Hurry!

128
00:06:30,930 --> 00:06:32,820
(snorts)

129
00:06:39,690 --> 00:06:41,240
(gasps)

130
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:44,440
Can I stop now, Hydia?
Please!

131
00:06:44,450 --> 00:06:45,750
No, one more lap.

132
00:06:45,750 --> 00:06:49,590
Because of you the little ponies
almost escaped.

133
00:06:49,590 --> 00:06:52,260
Yeah, sister dear.
(crunches)

134
00:06:52,250 --> 00:06:54,120
They almost got away.
(crunches)

135
00:06:56,630 --> 00:06:57,880
She heard me.

136
00:06:57,880 --> 00:07:00,140
She didn't mean to disobey you,
Hydia.

137
00:07:00,130 --> 00:07:01,430
It was really our fault.

138
00:07:01,430 --> 00:07:05,680
Yeah. Gee, we were only trying
to teach her some magic tricks.

139
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:08,680
I'll teach the tricks
in my family, okay?

140
00:07:09,940 --> 00:07:11,800
Everybody is a magician.

141
00:07:15,310 --> 00:07:17,690
The Flutter Ponies
are coming back.

142
00:07:17,700 --> 00:07:19,040
What?

143
00:07:19,030 --> 00:07:20,360
(gasps)

144
00:07:20,370 --> 00:07:22,960
I said, the Flutter Ponies
are coming back.

145
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,450
Listen.

146
00:07:26,710 --> 00:07:29,670
It is the Flutter Ponies.

147
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:31,320
(cheers)

148
00:07:31,330 --> 00:07:33,750
There's still time
to save Flutter Valley.

149
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:38,260
Shut up! There's no time
to save anything.

150
00:07:38,250 --> 00:07:39,500
It's almost sunset.

151
00:07:39,500 --> 00:07:42,420
We've got to stop them,
Hydia.

152
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:45,720
What if they have the Sunstone?

153
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,010
Ahhg!

154
00:07:47,010 --> 00:07:50,480
Roooooaaaaggghhrr!

155
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:55,180
Guard the entrance.
Don't let anyone in. Nobody.

156
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:56,520
Rooaaaagghhrr!

157
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:03,070
Oh no. Not Ahhg.
They'll never get past him.

158
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:07,790
But Hydia, don't you remember
what happened the last time?

159
00:08:07,780 --> 00:08:10,200
Of course I remember.

160
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:13,330
And Ahhg won't be tickled again.

161
00:08:13,340 --> 00:08:15,210
Come here, Ahhgy.

162
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:17,700
I've got something for you.

163
00:08:18,870 --> 00:08:20,620
Roooaaaaggghhrr!

164
00:08:23,960 --> 00:08:27,350
Drink this,
my little Ahhgy.

165
00:08:27,350 --> 00:08:31,130
And we won't have anything
to fear from Megan

166
00:08:31,140 --> 00:08:33,560
and the Flutter Ponies.

167
00:08:35,610 --> 00:08:36,820
