He's blocking the way.

169
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:45,480
Rooooaaagghr!

170
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,870
Not you again?

171
00:08:46,870 --> 00:08:49,700
Rooooaaaaghr!

172
00:08:49,710 --> 00:08:51,080
