173
00:08:51,070 --> 00:08:53,570
but we can't carry the Sunstone.

174
00:08:54,660 --> 00:08:55,740
It's too heavy.

175
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:59,580
We'll never make it
in time now.

176
00:08:59,580 --> 00:09:03,250
Not to worry. I know just
how to handle Ahhg.

177
00:09:06,090 --> 00:09:08,300
We found out he's ticklish.

178
00:09:08,310 --> 00:09:09,570
All you have to do is tickle him

179
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,310
and he'll fold up
like an accordion.

180
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,740
Coochy coochy coo!

181
00:09:18,020 --> 00:09:19,270
Maybe if we all do it...

182
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:22,570
Coochy coochy coo!

183
00:09:22,570 --> 00:09:23,740
Coochy coochy coo!

184
00:09:23,740 --> 00:09:28,270
I don't understand.
It worked last time.

185
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:30,870
Rooooaaaaghr!

186
00:09:30,860 --> 00:09:33,000
We'll never get past him.

187
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:35,160
And it's almost sunset.

188
00:09:35,170 --> 00:09:37,340
What are we going to do?

189
